      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't even feel real. like i'm watching someone else's life disappear. people always say \"it gets better\" or \"just work harder\" but there isn't anything left to work with. i've hit a wall and i honestly don't think i want to find a way around it. it just feels like i've reached the end of the road.",
